erge.com/e/23960876&quot;>;低于 100 美元&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/23962309&quot;>;不到 50 美元&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ReER1n&quot;>;在这里，我们汇总了 Prime 会员日的首选，价格仅为 25 美元或以下。其中一些可能是乏味的必需品，例如 USB-C 充电线，但您可能会惊讶于您可以使用什么样的技术......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/7/16/24198756/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24198756/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24198756/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T18:55:06-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T18:55:06-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊设备上最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;最新的 Echo Show 8 面向摄像头，屏幕打开。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/smk309xkHbPQQ8vEIxEDDP5_wVg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73457589/236901_Echo_Show_8_review_JTuohy_ 0012.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊在一些 Echo 设备上免费赠送智能灯泡，包括最新的 Echo Show 8。&lt;/em>; |图片：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mw5UEg&quot;>;2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 已正式到来。我们已经发布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;>;最佳 Prime Day 优惠的详细指南&lt;/ a>;，但如果您只是对亚马逊设备感兴趣，那么您可以在这里找到真正值得的设备。从基于 Alexa 的 Echo 智能扬声器到视频门铃，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/events/devicedeals?discounts-widget=%2522%257B%255C%2522state%255C%2522%253A%257B %255C%2522refinementFilters%255C%2522%253A%257B%257D%257D%252C%255C%2522version%255C%2522%253A1%257D%2522&quot;>;亚马逊正在为各种小工具打折&lt;/a>;，其中一些目前看到的是迄今为止的最低价格。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;BfmcmJ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;m8mKVO&quot;>;当然，这里主要需要注意的是，您必须是活跃的 Amazon Prime 会员才能享受所有 Prime Day 优惠。幸运的是，亚马逊&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21493780/amazon-prime-sign-up-day-deals-sale-price-free&quot;>;让注册变得非常容易&lt;/a>; ，特别是新会员可以通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/amazonprime/&quot;>;30 天免费试用&lt;/a>;享受独家折扣。&lt;/p>; &lt;div>; &lt;aside id=&quot;iAw8iv&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的最佳亚马逊 Prime Day 科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;了解以下产品的价格匹配政策百思买、塔吉特、沃尔玛等&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21570383/price-matching-policy-apple-google-microsoft&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt; /aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;kciix7&quot;>;最佳流媒体设备和电视优惠&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;OYrDFV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12140365&quot;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div id=&quot;P3RMT1&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12085801&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;fpt8SS&quot;>;如果您&#39;正在寻找...&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles- fire-tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles-fire-tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles-fire-tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T18:40:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T18:40:55-04:00</updated><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 正在将 X 和 SpaceX 迁往德克萨斯州</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;埃隆·马斯克的照片拼贴画。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VVS7kTIh5EGe9ZjuLdbK9sJA6yE=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464778/STK022_ELON_MUSK_CVIRGINIA_C.0。 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge |摄影：STR / NurPhoto、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;1K36Q1&quot;>;埃隆·马斯克表示，他计划将 X 和 SpaceX 的总部从加利福尼亚州迁至德克萨斯州。马斯克 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/ elonmusk/status/1813290895334383820&quot;>;在推文中写道&lt;/a>;，引用了&lt;a href=&quot;https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/billTextClient.xhtml?bill_id=202320240AB1955&quot;>;加州安全法案 (AB1955) ）&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;D3qbCb&quot;>;加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 于周一签署，禁止学校实施要求教师在未经学生许可的情况下披露学生性别认同变化的规定，并禁止对学生进行报复拒绝让学生出去的老师，报告&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2024-07-15/newsom-bans-schools-from-requiring-that-parents-are -notified-about-student-gender-identity&quot;>;&lt;em>;洛杉矶时报&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5chPYl&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x. com/elonmusk/status/1813295489032622586&quot;>;几分钟后，马斯克的另一篇帖子&lt;/a>;表示，目前总部位于旧金山的 X“将搬到……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24200039/elon-musk-moving-x-spacex-headquarters-texas&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24200039/elon-musk-moving-x-spacex-headquarters-texas" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24200039/elon-musk-moving-x-spacex-headquarters-texas</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T18:26:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T18:26:30-04:00</updated><title>仅需 100 美元或更少即可获得最佳 Prime Day 科技优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;珊瑚色和金色 Fitbit Charge 6 正面视图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SqjAfVJ25K7X5vUFgunGrLoEl0E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464052/236838_Fitbit_Charge_6_AKrales_0180.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcapt