ruise Critic&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 在 7 月 19 日投入服务之前已经预览了这些设施。其中包括名为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.royalcaribbean.com/cruise-dining/royal-railway-utopia-station&quot;>;皇家铁路乌托邦站&lt;/a>;的独特体验，乘客可以在虚拟火车上用餐一边乘坐，一边盯着大屏幕上飞驰而过的模拟风景。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WJDa2G&quot;>;这家餐厅看起来像两辆全尺寸的有轨电车，内饰豪华，两侧排列着四人包厢，每个都有自己的巨型显示屏作为虚拟窗口。食客从这些虚拟窗口看到的东西将全年轮换。第一个体验是西部主题，可以看到山脉、峡谷和淘金小镇的景色。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;Cx2VA2&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;位置：相对；padding-bottom：56.25%;&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Ro3Pbo&quot;>;&lt;q>;谋杀在...&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of -the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of-the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of-the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:02:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:02:54-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的无线耳机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 WF-1000XM5 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e6t1Ea8VCnt9pPlNtEqC2_bCfCc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67005648/DSCF2232.22.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;来自 Apple、Bose、三星、索尼、Beats、Google 等的最佳产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-1